                <note type="updated" update="general" import="tengyur-data-3824-3980_PH_new_v2.4.xml" date-time="2021-11-02T14:13:45.147Z" user="admin">The colophon notes that the contents of the text were drawn from the “the chapter on the ten grounds” (sa bcu'i le'u), presumably the Daśabhūmika-sūtra,
